  "prompt": "Which hashtag will I use to get more likes in Instagram?",
  "response": "Getting more likes on Instagram can depend on several factors, including the content of your post, your target audience, and current trends. However, here are some popular and generally effective hashtags that can help boost your visibility:\n\n1. #love\n2. #instagood\n3. #photooftheday\n4. #fashion\n5. #beautiful\n6. #art\n7. #happy\n8. #cute\n9. #travel\n10. #nature\n11. #like4like\n12. #followme\n13. #picoftheday\n14. #selfie\n15. #style\n16. #me\n17. #summer\n18. #fitness\n19. #food\n20. #instadaily\n\nIt's a good idea to mix popular hashtags with more niche or specific ones relevant to your post. Additionally, staying updated on current trends and incorporating hashtags related to trending topics can also help boost engagement. Tools like Instagram's Explore page, hashtag research tools, and even observing what hashtags influencers use can give you additional insights.",
